      • compareTo

        public int compareTo(EnergyAmount other)
        This method compareTos the value of this energy amount with another energy amount, taking into account the unit in which the other energy amount is expressed. If this energy amount is of lower value than the other, the method returns -1. If this energy amount is equal to the other, the method returns 0. If this energy amount is bigger than the other, the method returns 1.
